<taxonomicName authorityName="Blyth" authorityYear="1862" box="[2352,2476,1027,1060]" class="Mammalia" family="Viverridae" genus="Viverra" kingdom="Animalia" order="Carnivora" pageId="4" pageNumber="211" phylum="Chordata" rank="species" species="megaspila">megaspila</taxonomicName>
, but they are now believed to be separate species. Monotypic.
</paragraph>
